  ${
    gcdaddmlem.1 $e |- K e. ZZ $.
    gcdaddmlem.2 $e |- M e. ZZ $.
    gcdaddmlem.3 $e |- N e. ZZ $.
    $( Lemma for ~ gcdaddm . $)
    gcdaddmlem $p |- ( M gcd N ) = ( M gcd ( ( K x. M ) + N ) ) $=
